        sint molestias perspiciatis dolores est earum vero a reprehenderit
        magnam eveniet nobis! Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Inventore
        commodi, totam porro molestiae, cumque quaerat dolorem, possimus quam
        sint molestias perspiciatis dolores est earum vero a reprehenderit
        magnam eveniet nobis!
      </p>
      <a href='#contact' class='about-link'> Skontaktuj siÄ™ z nami</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: left;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .about-welcome {
    font-family: var(--dance-font);
    margin-top: 60px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: var(--main-pink);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .about-welcome-flower {
    background-image: url('../../assets/flower.png');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size:contain;
    width: 15%;
    height: 70px;
  }
  .about-welcome-text {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  }
  .about-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .text-wrapper {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 0px 5px 0px 5px;
  }
  .text-header {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-family: var(--logo-font);
    color: var(--text-font);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }
  .text {
    font-family: var(--main-font);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-font);
    line-height: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about-link {
    justify-content: center;
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    font-family: var(--main-font);
    margin-top: 30px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    max-width: 300px;
    padding: 14px 22px;
    color: var(--text-font);
    outline: 1px solid var(--text-font);
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 10px;
    
    transition: 0.3s background ease;
    background: transparent;
  }
  .about-link:hover {
    outline: none;
    color: var(--bg-white);
    background-color: var(--main-pink);
  }
  .about-image-wrapper {
    margin-top: 30px;
    display: flex;
    width: fit-content;
    align-items: center;
    order: 1;
  }
  .about-image {
    max-width: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 5px 50px 5px 50px;
  }
  .bg-title,
  .bg-subtitle {
    display: none;
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .about-section {
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 60px;
    }
    .about-container {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
      justify-content: space-around;
      margin-top: 40px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .bg-title,
    .bg-subtitle {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: fit-content;
      position: absolute;
      font-size: clamp(15rem, 24vw, 24rem);
      top: -3%;
      left: 13%;
      color: rgb(221, 208, 208);
      font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
      letter-spacing: 18px;
      opacity: 0.2;
      z-index: -10;
    }
    .bg-title {
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .bg-subtitle {
      color: #ebb7d2;
      top: 42%;
      left: 43%;
    }
    .text-wrapper {
      margin-left: 15px;
      width: 50%;
      padding: 35px;
    }
    .text-header {
      font-size:3rem
    }
    .about-image-wrapper {
      order: 0;
      min-width: 40%;
    }
    .about-image {
      min-width: 70%;
    }
  }
</style>
